Package armyc2.c5isr.renderer.utilities

Class MilStdSymbol

java.lang.Object
armyc2.c5isr.renderer.utilities.MilStdSymbol
public class MilStdSymbol extends Object
Object that holds information on how to draw a multipoint symbol after WebRenderer.RenderMultiPointAsMilStdSymbol(String, String, String, String, String, String, double, String, Map, Map) is called.
